dct_title_s: Tabula geographica, in qua regiones Cananaeae, et locorum situs prout ea tempore Christi, et Apostolorum fuerunt de integro describuntur, ac suis Limitibus distinguntur
dct_description_sm: Auctore Petro Plancio. Gedruckt tAmstelredam by Jan Evertss Cloppenborch ... Baptista Doetechmius sculp.
Added title in Dutch, the same title.

From a Dutch Bible. Leyden, Jan Bouwertss, 1609. "voor het Evangelium Matthei". The fifth map of the series of six biblical maps, first published in the so- called "Plancius Bible" in Amsterdam by Laurens Jacobszon in 1590.
Dutch text on both sides of verso.
